  "title": "SENIOR CHEMIST, PHARMACEUTICAL",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>TO CARRY OUT QC TESTS INCLUDING RAW MATERIALS TESTING, CHECKING OF PACKAGING MATERIALS, IN-PROCESS TEST, FINISHED PRODUCT TESTS.</li>\n  <li>TO CREATE, UPDATE AND MAINTAIN DOCUMENTS RELATED TO COMPANY'S PRODUCTS, SOPs, QC, QA, ETC</li>\n  <li>TO ENSURE ALL QC STAFF ARE APPROPRIATELY TRAINED AND QUALIFIED TO EXECUTE THE DUTIES ASSIGNED TO THEM WITH RESPECT TO cGMP &amp; QC related aspects.</li>\n  <li>TO PERFORM STABILITY STUDIES OF PRODUCTS, VALIDATION PROJECTS, PRODUCT QUALITY REVIEWS IN COMPLIANCE WITH RELEVANT STANDARDS</li>\n  <li>TO ASSIST IN RESEARCH &amp; DEVELOPMENT NEEDS, EG. READING UP, RESEARCH, OBTAINING MATERIALS, MAKE SAMPLES, LABORATORY SCALE PRODUCTION, TESTING &amp; PREPARING SAMPLE EVALUATION REPORTS.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
